==Starting off==
===Talking to Otto for the first time===
* '''Otto Godblessed:''' Good day! You seem a hearty warrior. Maybe even some barbarian blood in that body of yours?
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|You think so?}}
** '''Player:''' You think so?
** '''Otto Godblessed:''' Who can tell? My forefathers weren't averse to travelling, so it is possible. They tended to cause too much trouble in your so-called civilised lands, however, so most returned to their ancestral homes.
** '''Otto Godblessed:''' In any case, given you seem the type, I think you are ready to learn our more secret tribal feats for yourself.
** '''Player:''' Oh, that sounds interesting. What sort of skills would these be?
** '''Otto Godblessed:''' To begin with, I can supply knowledge in the ways of firemaking, our special rod fishing tricks, a selection of spear skills and our agricultural techniques.
** '''Player:''' There are more advanced stages though, going by your description?
** '''Otto Godblessed:''' Your perception is creditable. I can eventually teach of more advanced firemaking techniques, and the rod fishing skills are but a preliminary to our special potions and brews.
** '''Otto Godblessed:''' These secrets must, however, wait until you have mastered the basics.
** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
** {{topt|Please teach me of your cunning with harpoons.}}
*** {{tact|below}}
** {{topt|What can I learn about the use of a fishing rod?}}
*** {{tact|below}}
** {{topt|I'm ready for your firemaking wisdom. Please instruct me.}}
*** {{tact|below}}
** {{topt|How can I use my strength in the ways of agriculture?}}
*** {{tact|below}}
** {{topt|I'd better get going.}}
*** '''Player:''' I'd better get going.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Who are you and why do you live all the way out here?}}
** '''Player:''' Who are you and why do you live all the way out here?
** '''Otto Godblessed:''' Me? I am Otto, known as the Godblessed. I follow the ways of our barbarian ancestors, communing with the spirits of the dead and teaching their ways to worthy disciples.
** '''Otto Godblessed:''' Perhaps you could be one of them. You look a likely sort to learn of these ways. As I say, you might even have a bit of barbarian blood hidden away in you.
** {{topt|You think so?}}
