===Speaking to Otto after learning of pyre ships===
* '''Otto Godblessed:''' Good day to you, hearty warrior! May the spirits guide you.
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|Let's talk about my training.}}
** '''Player:''' Let's talk about my training.
